// ──── EXACT READING PASSAGE TAPPABLE TOKENS (voice-engineer reference) ────
//
// 6 unique tappable Spanish tokens (one each, no repeats):
//   1. "Mi Gente"   — song title, masc. noun phrase (mi + gente)
//   2. "mi"         — 1st-person possessive, isolated
//   3. "tu"         — 2nd-person informal possessive, isolated
