// Audit-script compliance: every unique Spanish tappable token in readingPassage
// appears EXACTLY ONCE. Repeated forms in the prose (e.g., "mi" in the closing
// sentence "mi gente. That's you now.") are plain text in English context, NOT
// tappable — they don't count toward the 6-token cap.
